# ==============================================================================
# CATCHY BOT  - GIT IGNORE FILE
# ==============================================================================
# This file tells Git which files/folders to ignore (not track)
# These files should NOT be committed to version control
#
# Why? They contain:
# - Sensitive data (passwords, API keys)
# - Generated files (can be recreated)
# - Local configuration (different per developer)
# - Large files (database dumps, media uploads)
# ==============================================================================



