# NOTES
# ==============================================================================
#
# HOW TO USE:
# 1. This file is already in effect once committed
# 2. To stop tracking a file already committed:
#    git rm --cached filename
# 3. To check what's ignored:
#    git status --ignored
# 4. To add exception for ignored file:
#    git add -f filename
#
# IMPORTANT:
# - Always commit this file FIRST before any other files
# - Review regularly and update as project grows
# - Never remove .env from this list!
#
# ==============================================================================